1. (optional) Download and install Java 
2. Add Java bin to path
3. Download Nifi: http://httpd-mirror.sergal.org/apache/nifi/1.8.0/nifi-1.8.0-bin.tar.gz
4. untar nifi to /etc 
5. modify /etc/nifi-1.8.0/conf/nifi.properties, set the available port for nifi
6. start nifi: /etc/nifi-1.8.0/bin/nifi.sh start

Nifi will be started on the selected port
7. open Nifi: <host>:<port> in browser
